  title="Prolotherapy Treatment"
  description="Prolotherapy is a regenerative injection therapy that uses concentrated dextrose to trigger natural tissue healing. Learn about prolotherapy for arthritis, tendon injuries, and back pain at MacLeod Naturopathic in Halifax."
