          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-950 mb-2">Recovery</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                You may experience some soreness for 1-3 days after treatment—this is a normal part of the healing response. Most patients can continue normal activities, though we recommend avoiding anti-inflammatory medications which can interfere with healing.
              </p>
