        <details class="group bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 font-serif font-semibold text-emerald-950">
            Is prolotherapy painful?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-700 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
